{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"explicitAlignment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"of","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"guide","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"HorizontalAlignment","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/HorizontalAlignment","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore19HorizontalAlignmentV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"in","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"bounds","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CGRect","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CGRect","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"proposal","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ProposedViewSize","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ProposedViewSize","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore16ProposedViewSizeV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"subviews","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AnyLayout","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnyLayoutV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":".","kind":"text"},{"text":"Subviews","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Layout\/Subviews","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore6LayoutP8Subviewsa","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"cache","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AnyLayout","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnyLayoutV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":".","kind":"text"},{"text":"Cache","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout\/Cache","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnyLayoutV5CacheV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CGFloat","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/HorizontalAlignment","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" guide that the method calculates"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the position of."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"guide"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The region that the container view’s parent allocates to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"container view, specified in the parent’s coordinate space.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"bounds"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A proposed size for the container.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"proposal"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A collection of proxy instances that represent the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"views arranged by the container. You can use the proxies in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"collection to get information about the subviews as you determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"where to place the guide."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"subviews"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Optional storage for calculated data that you can share among","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the methods of your custom layout container. See","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout\/makeCache(subviews:)","isActive":true},{"text":" for details.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"cache"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"return-value","level":2,"text":"Return Value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The guide’s position relative to the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"bounds"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Return "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" to indicate that the guide doesn’t have an explicit"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Implement this method to return a value for the specified alignment","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"guide of a custom layout container. The value you return affects","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the placement of the container as a whole, but it doesn’t affect how the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"container arranges subviews relative to one another.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can use this method to put an alignment guide in a nonstandard","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"position. For example, you can indent the container’s leading edge","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"alignment guide by 10 points:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["extension BasicVStack {","    func explicitAlignment(","        of guide: HorizontalAlignment,","        in bounds: CGRect,","        proposal: ProposedViewSize,","        subviews: Subviews,","        cache: inout ()","    ) -> CGFloat? {","        if guide == .leading {","            return bounds.minX + 10","        }","        return nil","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The above example returns "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" for other guides to indicate that they"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"don’t have an explicit value. A guide without an explicit value behaves"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as it would for any other view. If you don’t implement the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method, the protocol’s default implementation merges the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"subviews’ guides."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout\/explicitAlignment(of:in:proposal:subviews:cache:)-2vuj4","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Layout\/AnyLayout.swift#L430","fileName":"AnyLayout.swift"},"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnyLayoutV17explicitAlignment2of2in8proposal8subviews5cache14CoreFoundation7CGFloatVSgAA010HorizontalG0V_So6CGRectVAA16ProposedViewSizeVAA0E8SubviewsVAC5CacheVztF","title":"explicitAlignment(of:in:proposal:subviews:cache:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"explicitAlignment"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"of"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore19HorizontalAlignmentV","text":"HorizontalAlignment"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"in"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CGRect","text":"CGRect"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"proposal"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore16ProposedViewSizeV","text":"ProposedViewSize"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"subviews"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{